dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines and spot heights. "2-43." "113603." Northern Italy Grid - Convergence. Shows railways, roads, canals, power lines, churches, and state, province, district, and commune boundaries. "Published by War Office, 1943." Reprinted 1943 by A.M.S. United States. Army Map Service AMS 1. Reprinted 1943 by A.M.S. Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. Provisional G.S.G.S. no. 4380 In upper left margin: "Italy."
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1942.
